{"FUEGIAN":[{"def":"Of or pertaining to Terra del Fuego.","pos":""},{"def":"A native of Terra del Fuego.","pos":""}],"FUEL":[{"def":"Any matter used to produce heat by burning; that which feeds fire; combustible matter used for fires, as wood, coal, peat, etc.","pos":""},{"def":"Anything that serves to feed or increase passion or excitement.","pos":""}],"FUELER":[{"def":"One who, or that which, supplies fuel.","pos":""}]}